fields.name: HOMLUX Dimmable Rectangular LED Bathroom Mirror Auto-off Anti-fogging and 3 color with Smart Touch Control
fields.description: Explore the HOMLUX Smart LED Bathroom Mirror, a pinnacle of exceptional design and cutting-edge functionality. It boasts a 5mm copper-free silver technology, presenting both eco-friendliness and long-lasting durability. Through intelligent wall switch and memory touch sensor, control without physical contact reaches new heights of convenience. The 1.18-inch ultra-thin design balances fashion and space, catering to your bathroom needs in 360 degrees. UL and ETL-certified components ensure safety, while the unique anti-fog technology, coupled with 240 LEDs/m backlighting, maintains a clear and bright mirror surface. Dimming from 5% to 100%, as well as color temperature choices of 3000K, 4500K, and 6000K, create the perfect ambiance. Flicker-free, UV-free, eye-protective comfort turns every glimpse into a delightful experience. The HOMLUX Smart LED Bathroom Mirror revolutionizes your bathroom experience, seamlessly merging elegance and intelligence.
fields.bullet_1: Smart Controls & Stay Fog-Free：Turn the lights on and off without touching the mirror – the wall switch and mirror touch switch are interconnected and feature memory functions. Say goodbye to post-shower fog. Built-in defogger ensures the LED vanity mirror stays clear and fog-free, the anti-fog switches are a separate control, which is safe and energy-saving, auto-shutting off after an hour.
fields.bullet_2: Customizable Lighting：Our 240 LED lamp beads per meter provide a super bright 12V backlight, bringing your bathroom to life while keeping the energy bill low. Adjust the brightness from 5% to 100% by holding down the power switch button for 2-3 seconds, and choose from cozy 3000K warm light, 4500K natural light, or 6000K bright white to set the mood right.
fields.bullet_3: Comfort for Your Eyes: We've ensured a flicker-free experience with no UV rays. Press and hold for 3 seconds to turn off the blue light standby display of the mirror, making every glance a pleasure.
fields.bullet_4: Safety First & Built to Last: An explosion-proof film is added to the mirror's surface to prevent breakage and minimize potential harm. All electronic parts are UL-certified, and the whole unit boasts an ETL certification, ensuring peace of mind for you and your family. With an impressive lifespan of over 120,000 hours, this mirror isn't just a purchase; it's an investment in quality.
fields.bullet_5: Versatile Installation: Whether you prefer it horizontally or vertically, our handy Z-type aluminum strips make mounting a breeze.
fields.assembly_details: Adult Assembly Required, Some Tools Provided

fields.bullet_1: Smart Controls & Stay Fog-Free：Turn the lights on and off without touching the mirror – the wall switch and mirror touch switch are interconnected and feature memory functions. Say goodbye to post-shower fog. Built-in defogger ensures the LED vanity mirror stays clear and fog-free, the anti-fog switches are a separate control, which is safe and energy-saving, auto-shutting off after an hour.
fields.bullet_2: Customizable Lighting：Our 240 LED lamp beads per meter provide a super bright 12V backlight, bringing your bathroom to life while keeping the energy bill low. With an impressive lifespan of over 120,000 hours, this mirror isn't just a purchase; it's an investment in quality.

fields.name: HOMLUX Dog Grooming Table
fields.description: Elevate the grooming experience for your pet with the HOMLUX Dog Grooming Table, designed for comfort and convenience. Featuring a waterproof, non-slip MDF surface and an adjustable H-shaped arm, it easily accommodates pets of all sizes. The foldable leg design, equipped with non-slip rubber feet, ensures stability and safety while allowing for easy storage and transport. Additionally, a dedicated storage basket keeps grooming tools and accessories organized.
fields.bullet_1: Adjustable Grooming Arm: Secure H-shaped design with an easy-to-adjust knob, suitable for pets of any size.
fields.bullet_2: Waterproof Non-Slip Surface: High-quality MDF material with a waterproof coating and rounded corners for maximum safety.
fields.bullet_3: Convenient Storage Basket: Removable 25.6" x 12.6" basket with a capacity of 22 lbs, keeping grooming essentials within reach.
fields.bullet_4: Portable and Easy to Store: Foldable legs and triangular brackets provide stability, perfect for mobility and indoor use.
fields.bullet_5: Safe and Sturdy: Thick tabletop with non-slip rubber feet, maintaining stability on smooth surfaces.
fields.prop_65_warning: WARNING: This product contains chemicals known to the state of California to cause cancer, and birth defects or other reproductive harm.For more information: www.P65Warnings.ca.gov

fields.name: HOMLUX Pull-Out 2 Tier Home Organizer with Sliding Track in the Middle
fields.description: The HOMLUX Pull-Out 2 Tier Home Organizer is a game-changer for modern kitchens. Designed meticulously with a central sliding track, this metal pullout basket ensures maximum utilization of cabinet space. Enjoy double the storage with its two-tier system, perfect for organizing all your kitchen necessities. Its unique latch design simplifies installation; with just a few screws, you can mount it either on the cabinet bottom or a fixed shelf. Durability is paramount, with solid connecting rods reinforcing its structure. Coupled with an industrial-grade ball bearing glide system, expect nothing less than smooth, silent operation every time. Experience a decluttered kitchen with HOMLUX.
fields.bullet_1: Double the Organization: With two tiers and a unique sliding track in the middle, the HOMLUX organizer effectively doubles your storage capacity, ensuring every kitchen essential has its designated spot
fields.bullet_2: Easy Installation: Forget complicated setups! The HOMLUX organizer boasts a unique latch design, requiring just a few screws. Whether mounted on the cabinet bottom or a fixed shelf, installation is swift and straightforward.
fields.bullet_3: Sturdy & Reliable: Constructed with solid connecting rods, this organizer stands strong under the weight of your kitchen tools. Trust in its lasting power to withstand daily use and wear.
fields.bullet_4: Smooth Operation: Say goodbye to jarring movements! Thanks to its industrial-grade ball bearing glide system, this organizer promises a smooth, quiet, and hassle-free slide every time.
fields.bullet_5: Versatile Placement: Flexibility at its finest. Whether you want it on the cabinet bottom or fixed shelf, the HOMLUX Pull-Out Organizer adapts to your needs, making it the ideal fit for various cabinet layouts.

fields.name: HOMLUX Pull-Out 2 Tier Home Organizer, slide out single
fields.description: Streamline your kitchen with the HOMLUX Pull-Out 2 Tier Home Organizer. Designed for efficiency, these shelves effortlessly slide out, granting easy access to kitchen essentials while optimizing cabinet storage. The latest version boasts enhanced sliding mechanisms and innovative mounting, supporting up to 100 pounds and maximizing lower space. Swift installation is guaranteed with the included template and screws, offering a seamless organization solution.
fields.bullet_1: Perfectly designed for base cabinets, this 2 Tier home organizer seamlessly fits into most cabinets that are 12.5 inches wide or larger, maximizing your storage space
fields.bullet_2: Featuring full-extension ball-bearing slides, this organizer is built tough, supporting up to an impressive 100 lbs - perfect for those hefty pots, pans, and other kitchen essentials.
fields.bullet_3: Say goodbye to tedious setups. With our intuitive template and a handful of screws, you'll have this organizer set up and ready to use in a mere 15 minutes.
fields.bullet_4: With two tiers, segregate and locate your kitchenware or any items easily, ensuring a clutter-free and systematic storage solution.
fields.bullet_5: Built with quality in mind, the organizer ensures longevity while its sleek design complements any home interior, merging utility with aesthetics.

fields.name: HOMLUX Pull-Out 2 Tier Home Organizer with Sliding Track in the Middle
fields.description: The HOMLUX Pull-Out 2 Tier Home Organizer is the epitome of space-saving brilliance. Designed specifically for narrow kitchen cabinets, this slide-out spice rack can even nestle seamlessly between two cabinets, ensuring every inch of your kitchen is used efficiently. Say goodbye to bending or shuffling items; with its slide-out feature, spices and sauces are always within easy grasp. Each of its two tiers is meticulously crafted to house your culinary essentials, ensuring better organization and accessibility. Durability meets smoothness with its advanced sliding system, ensuring silent operation each time. Plus, with an easy installation process requiring just a few screws, your kitchen can transform into an organized haven in no time. Elevate your cooking experience with HOMLUX.
fields.bullet_1: Optimized for Narrow Spaces: Specially designed for narrow kitchen cabinets, the HOMLUX organizer is the perfect fit between two cabinets, making efficient use of limited space and transforming it into an organized oasis
fields.bullet_2: Hassle-Free Access: No more bending or rummaging! The slide-out design ensures all your spices and sauces are within easy reach, offering a quick and convenient cooking experience.
fields.bullet_3: Double-tiered Organization: With its 2-tier system, neatly categorize and access your spices, ensuring a clutter-free cabinet and easy-to-find ingredients every time you cook.
fields.bullet_4: Silent and Smooth Operation: Crafted for consistency, its durable design promises a seamless and quiet slide each time. Access your spices without any jarring or noise.
fields.bullet_5: Simple Installation: DIY-friendly setup! With its user-centric design, all it takes is a few screws, and your spice rack will be ready to transform your kitchen organization.

fields.name: HOMLUX Wood Slide-Out Shelf with Soft Close
fields.description: Store cabinet essentials within easy reach with a wood pullout shelf and maximize your cabinet space. No more back-breaking bending over and shifting items around to get to what you want, perfect for storing food containers, cans, cutting boards, pots and pans and spices and ect. Make sure you measure your cabinets correctly before purchasing.
fields.bullet_1: MEASURE YOU OPENING: Be sure to measure the width and depth of your cabinets correctly, Minimum cabinet opening: 15 in; Minimum cabinet depth: 24 in.
fields.bullet_2: MATERIAL: Made from birch with a natural clear coat finish. It is hard, strong, has good crushing strength and the drawer slides are rated for 100 lbs .
fields.bullet_3: NO ASSEMBLY REQUIRED: Pull out drawer comes fully assembled, simply install the slides on the drawers
fields.bullet_4: WHATS INCLUDED: Full installed 1 wood drawer ; 2 full extension SOFT CLOSE drawer; slides; Mounting screws; Installation Template and Users manual
fields.bullet_5: SOFT CLOSE: The soft colse slide out cabinet organizer are made of thick steel slides, full extension, smooth and quiet,maintaining protection and a more tranquil home environment

fields.name: NEO Chair N-GEN Gaming Chair
fields.description: The NEO CHAIR mesh chair is the perfect combination of versatility, comfort, and quality. Designed with convenience in mind, it features padded armrests that can easily flip up to accommodate different sitting positions. The chair's breathable woven mesh material and ergonomic design provide excellent back support, promoting good posture and reducing fatigue. Additionally, the well-balanced cushion ensures all-day comfort, making it ideal for long hours of work or relaxation.
fields.bullet_1: Each body is unique. Instead of a fixed lumbar support cushion, N-GEN's LEVIS is upgraded with an adjustable lumbar cushion. Both the head and lumbar cushions are removable for versatile customization
fields.bullet_2: Feel the difference with N-GEN's signature seat design. Fullest fill for all-day comfort. Slightly contoured leveled seat for balanced support. Sit any way you like with the extra space.
fields.bullet_3: Made with soft & high-quality multi-layered PU leather. Resistant to scratches, stains, peeling, and cracking for easy maintenance. Finished with detailed embroidery.
fields.bullet_4: Smooth-rolling wheels. Durable & smooth gas lift cylinder. Powerfully supportive base. All tested over 10,000 times and certified for safety and quality.
fields.bullet_5: Apart from its advanced comfort features, the NEO CHAIR promises long-lasting durability, making it an ideal and reliable choice for any office or home workspace.

fields.name: Amazing Force Single Handle Pull Down Sprayer Kitchen Faucet with 2 Modes
fields.description: Durable & Superior Material - Are you trouble with replacing the faucet frequently before? Our kitchen pull-out faucet comes with a commercial SUS 304 stainless steel construction, and superior corrosion & rust-resistant finish. It exceeds industry longevity standards, ensuring durable performance for life. It has an NSF standard zinc alloy cover with multi-layer brushed nickel, as well as a high-temperature resistant EPDM hose.
fields.bullet_1: Dual Water Flow Modes for Customized Use: The Amazing Force Kitchen Faucet offers two tailor-made water flow settings—a delicate stream ideal for routine tasks like rinsing fruits, and a robust spray that effectively eliminates stubborn residues. These dual modes not only accommodate a variety of kitchen chores but also promote smart water consumption, striking the perfect balance between functionality and sustainability
fields.bullet_2: Ergonomic Pull-Down Design for Comprehensive Sink Coverage: Beyond its sleek appearance, the faucet's pull-down design is a game-changer. Whether it's filling large pots or cleaning the remote corners of your sink, its extended reach ensures optimal efficiency. By minimizing water splashes and reducing clean-up time, it truly revolutionizes kitchen routines.
fields.bullet_3: Intuitive Single-Handed Operation: The faucet boasts a single-handle mechanism, a testimony to its user-centric design. By seamlessly controlling water temperature and flow volume with one hand, users can multitask with the other, making kitchen activities more fluid and time-efficient.
fields.bullet_4: Streamlined Installation & Maintenance: Bid goodbye to cumbersome installations! The Amazing Force Faucet is designed with users in mind, complete with a pre-attached deck plate and pre-installed hoses. This feature not only simplifies the setup process but also ensures that the faucet aligns perfectly with your sink setup, eliminating any guesswork.
fields.bullet_5: Commitment to Durability and Quality: Wondering about its longevity? The faucet's construction speaks for itself. Built with commercial-grade SUS 304 stainless steel, it stands resilient against corrosion and rust, promising years of undiminished performance. The multi-layered brushed nickel cover meets NSF standards, and when paired with a high-temperature resistant EPDM hose, it solidifies the faucet's commitment to quality. Invest in the Amazing Force Faucet, and you're investing in a lifetime of reliable and aesthetic kitchen service.

fields.name: Rainovo Single Handle Pull Down Sprayer Kitchen Faucet with 2 Modes
fields.description: Elevate your kitchen experience with this state-of-the-art faucet, equipped with a 2-mode pull-down sprayer including two innovative features: BLADE and MIST. The BLADE mode boasts a robust, dense water flow, adept at tackling stubborn stains, while the MIST mode provides a gentle, wide coverage ideal for rinsing fruits. Marrying efficiency with a sleek design, this faucet promises to redefine your kitchen's functionality and aesthetic.
fields.bullet_1: Optimized Water Flow with Dual Modes: The Rainovo Kitchen Faucet boasts two distinct water flow settings — a gentle stream for everyday tasks like rinsing fruits or filling pots, and a forceful spray that efficiently handles tougher cleaning tasks. This thoughtful feature ensures you not only have versatility in usage but also promotes water conservation, aligning with today's need for eco-friendly appliances
fields.bullet_2: Sleek Design with Complete Mobility: The faucet's high arc design is complemented by a 360° rotation capability, ensuring maximum sink coverage and flexibility. fields.name: HOMLUX Dimmable Rectangular Frosted Edge Bathroom Mirror with Memory, Auto-off Anti-fogging and 3 color temperature
fields.description: Explore the HOMLUX Smart LED Bathroom Mirror, a pinnacle of exceptional design and cutting-edge functionality. It boasts a 5mm copper-free silver technology, presenting both eco-friendliness and long-lasting durability. Through intelligent wall switch and memory touch sensor, control without physical contact reaches new heights of convenience. The 1.18-inch ultra-thin design balances fashion and space, catering to your bathroom needs in 360 degrees. UL and ETL-certified components ensure safety, while the unique anti-fog technology, coupled with 240 LEDs/m backlighting, maintains a clear and bright mirror surface. Dimming from 5% to 100%, as well as color temperature choices of 3000K, 4500K, and 6000K, create the perfect ambiance. Flicker-free, UV-free, eye-protective comfort turns every glimpse into a delightful experience. The HOMLUX Smart LED Bathroom Mirror revolutionizes your bathroom experience, seamlessly merging elegance and intelligence.
fields.bullet_1: Smart Controls & Stay Fog-Free: Turn the lights on and off without touching the mirror – the wall switch and mirror touch switch are interconnected and feature memory functions. Say goodbye to post-shower fog. Built-in defogger ensures the LED vanity mirror stays clear and fog-free, the anti-fog switches are a separate control, which is safe and energy-saving, auto-shutting off after an hour
fields.bullet_2: Customizable Lighting：Our 240 LED lamp beads per meter provide a super bright 12V backlight, bringing your bathroom to life while keeping the energy bill low. Adjust the brightness from 5% to 100% by holding down the power switch button for 2-3 seconds, and choose from cozy 3000K warm light, 4500K natural light, or 6000K bright white to set the mood right.
fields.bullet_3: Comfort for Your Eyes: We've ensured a flicker-free experience with no UV rays. Press and hold for 3 seconds to turn off the blue light standby display of the mirror, making every glance a pleasure.
fields.bullet_4: Safety First & Built to Last: An explosion-proof film is added to the mirror's surface to prevent breakage and minimize potential harm. All electronic parts are UL-certified, and the whole unit boasts an ETL certification, ensuring peace of mind for you and your family. With an impressive lifespan of over 120,000 hours, this mirror isn't just a purchase; it's an investment in quality.
fields.bullet_5: Versatile Installation: Whether you prefer it horizontally or vertically, our handy Z-type aluminum strips make mounting a breeze.
fields.assembly_details: Adult Assembly Required, Some Tools Provided

Built-in defogger ensures the LED vanity mirror stays clear and fog-free, the anti-fog switches are a separate control, which is safe and energy-saving, auto-shutting off after an hour
fields.bullet_2: Customizable Lighting：Our 240 LED lamp beads per meter provide a super bright 12V backlight, bringing your bathroom to life while keeping the energy bill low. Adjust the brightness from 5% to 100% by holding down the power switch button for 2-3 seconds, and choose from cozy 3000K warm light, 4500K natural light, or 6000K bright white to set the mood right.
fields.bullet_3: Comfort for Your Eyes: We've ensured a flicker-free experience with no UV rays. Press and hold for 3 seconds to turn off the blue light standby display of the mirror, making every glance a pleasure.
fields.bullet_4: Safety First & Built to Last: An explosion-proof film is added to the mirror's surface to prevent breakage and minimize potential harm. All electronic parts are UL-certified, and the whole unit boasts an ETL certification, ensuring peace of mind for you and your family. With an impressive lifespan of over 120,000 hours, this mirror isn't just a purchase; it's an investment in quality.
fields.bullet_5: Versatile Installation: Whether you prefer it horizontally or vertically, our handy Z-type aluminum strips make mounting a breeze.
fields.assembly_details: Adult Assembly Required, Some Tools Provided

Built-in defogger ensures the LED vanity mirror stays clear and fog-free, the anti-fog switches are a separate control, which is safe and energy-saving, auto-shutting off after an hour.
fields.bullet_2: Customizable Lighting：Our 240 LED lamp beads per meter provide a super bright 12V backlight, bringing your bathroom to life while keeping the energy bill low. Adjust the brightness from 5% to 100% by holding down the power switch button for 2-3 seconds, and choose from cozy 3000K warm light, 4500K natural light, or 6000K bright white to set the mood right.
fields.bullet_3: Comfort for Your Eyes: We've ensured a flicker-free experience with no UV rays. Press and hold for 3 seconds to turn off the blue light standby display of the mirror, making every glance a pleasure.
fields.bullet_4: Safety First & Built to Last: An explosion-proof film is added to the mirror's surface to prevent breakage and minimize potential harm. All electronic parts are UL-certified, and the whole unit boasts an ETL certification, ensuring peace of mind for you and your family. With an impressive lifespan of over 120,000 hours, this mirror isn't just a purchase; it's an investment in quality.
fields.bullet_5: Versatile Installation: Whether you prefer it horizontally or vertically, our handy Z-type aluminum strips make mounting a breeze.
fields.assembly_details: Adult Assembly Required, Some Tools Provided

Through intelligent wall switch and memory touch sensor, control without physical contact reaches new heights of convenience. The 1.18-inch ultra-thin design balances fashion and space, catering to your bathroom needs in 360 degrees. UL and ETL-certified components ensure safety, while the unique anti-fog technology, coupled with 240 LEDs/m backlighting, maintains a clear and bright mirror surface. Dimming from 5% to 100%, as well as color temperature choices of 3000K, 4500K, and 6000K, create the perfect ambiance. Flicker-free, UV-free, eye-protective comfort turns every glimpse into a delightful experience. The HOMLUX Smart LED Bathroom Mirror revolutionizes your bathroom experience, seamlessly merging elegance and intelligence.
fields.bullet_1: Smart Controls & Stay Fog-Free: Turn the lights on and off without touching the mirror – the wall switch and mirror touch switch are interconnected and feature memory functions. Say goodbye to post-shower fog. Built-in defogger ensures the LED vanity mirror stays clear and fog-free, the anti-fog switches are a separate control, which is safe and energy-saving, auto-shutting off after an hour
fields.bullet_2: Customizable Lighting：Our 240 LED lamp beads per meter provide a super bright 12V backlight, bringing your bathroom to life while keeping the energy bill low. Adjust the brightness from 5% to 100% by holding down the power switch button for 2-3 seconds, and choose from cozy 3000K warm light, 4500K natural light, or 6000K bright white to set the mood right.
fields.bullet_3: Comfort for Your Eyes: We've ensured a flicker-free experience with no UV rays. Press and hold for 3 seconds to turn off the blue light standby display of the mirror, making every glance a pleasure.
fields.bullet_4: Safety First & Built to Last: An explosion-proof film is added to the mirror's surface to prevent breakage and minimize potential harm. All electronic parts are UL-certified, and the whole unit boasts an ETL certification, ensuring peace of mind for you and your family. With an impressive lifespan of over 120,000 hours, this mirror isn't just a purchase; it's an investment in quality.
fields.bullet_5: Versatile Installation: Whether you prefer it horizontally or vertically, our handy Z-type aluminum strips make mounting a breeze.
fields.assembly_details: Adult Assembly Required, Some Tools Provided

This pull-out basket is designed to be installed at the base of your kitchen cabinet. With smooth ball-bearing slides and a sturdy base, it stays in place as you pull the basket out. This kitchen organizer has a capacity to hold up to 55 pounds. The pull-out kitchen cabinet organizer comes with the necessary mounting hardware. fields.name: HOMLUX Pull-Out Pantry Drawer Cabinet Organizer
fields.description: This elegantly designed Drawer Cabinet Organizer is your ultimate solution to reclaiming lost spaces. Slide out with ease and access those hard-to-reach cupboard and under-sink items, turning previously cluttered areas into efficient storage zones. Thanks to the heavy-duty ball bearing slides, each pull is a fluid, full-extension experience, bringing your items seamlessly to your fingertips. With an impressive 75 lbs capacity, our basket can handle a wide variety of items, ensuring you maximize your storage potential. And for those who fancy a touch of DIY, installation is a breeze. With just 4 screws (included), you'll have this set up in no time. Plus, for those looking to cater to different storage requirements, we offer multiple sizes, allowing you to choose the perfect fit for your space.
fields.bullet_1: Maximized Space Utilization: Elegantly crafted, this Drawer Cabinet Organizer effortlessly transforms previously wasted or hard-to-reach areas into efficient storage zones, ensuring every inch of your cabinet or under-sink space is optimally utilized.
fields.bullet_2: Fluid Access: Experience unparalleled accessibility with our heavy-duty ball-bearing slides. Each pull provides a smooth, full-extension movement, making sure all your items are brought forward without any fuss, revolutionizing your retrieval process.
fields.bullet_3: Outstanding Load Capacity: Boasting an impressive 75 lbs weight capacity, this organizer can accommodate a wide range of items, from bulky pots and pans to heavier pantry goods, ensuring your storage needs are met without compromise.
fields.bullet_4: Effortless Installation: No need for professional help. The organizer is designed with simplicity in mind, and with just four included screws, you can have it set up and ready to declutter in no time.
fields.bullet_5: Tailored to Your Needs: Recognizing that one size doesn't fit all, we offer the organizer in multiple dimensions. This ensures that regardless of your storage requirements or cabinet size, there's an option that's the perfect fit for your space.

fields.name: Homlux Pull Down Kitchen Faucet
fields.description: The single-handle pull-down faucet from updates your kitchen with its sleek style and superior functionality that is essential for every kitchen. Get ample kitchen space from its high-arc spout and a modern look with its stainless steel finish and curved minimalist design. Ergonomic, pull-down spray head provides a comfortable grip and push-button function to stream, spray and pause, while providing a 1.8 GPM rate for outstanding water flow. Faucets offers smooth operation, easy movement, self retraction, and secure docking, durable metal construction, copper finish for lasting durability. Its ceramic disc cartridge ensures drip-free performance. And the faucet is easy to install in any kitchen with 1 hole in the sink or countertop, making it the perfect choice for any faucet refresh.

fields.bullet_4: Ceramic disc valve assures smooth control and a lifetime of drip-free, maintenance-free performance
fields.bullet_5: Soft, rubber touch-clean spray holes

fields.name: Homlux Bathroom Faucet
fields.description: The bathroom faucet seamlessly ties your decor together. Transitional design that features a blend of gentle curves and clean lines is the perfect choice for an easy refresh or an entire remodel. The dual-handle design enables user-friendly hot and cold water temperature control. This classic design, with sturdy lever handles, is engineered for lasting durability and a lifetime of drip-free performance, a hallmark of every HomLux faucet. It also features the drain assembly for quick and simple installation.

fields.bullet_2: 3-hole deck-mount installation
fields.bullet_3: Ceramic disc valve assures smooth control and a lifetime of drip-free, maintenance-free performance
fields.bullet_4: 2-lever handles design, precise control over temperature and flow
fields.bullet_5: Includes matching press pop-up drain assembly

fields.name: Rainovo stainless steel Bathroom Towel Hook
fields.description: Experience the fusion of functionality and aesthetics with the Rainovo Bathroom Towel Hook. Crafted from premium-grade materials, this towel hook is designed not only to be an elegant addition to your space but also to withstand the challenges of humid environments. Its smooth brushed finish assures durability while preventing daily wear and tear, and its safety-focused design ensures peace of mind. The strong load-bearing capability combined with an easy, concealed installation process makes it an essential choice for modern bathrooms and kitchens.
fields.bullet_1: Durability at Its Best: Expertly designed all-metal construction that promises resistance to both corrosion and rust, making it a versatile choice for bathrooms, showers, or kitchens, regardless of humidity
fields.bullet_2: Elegant Yet Safe: The smooth brushed wall-mounted design elevates the aesthetic appeal while offering protection against daily abrasions. The deliberate rounded corners prioritize safety, minimizing potential hand injuries.

fields.name: WARMSTORM WiFi Electric Flannel Blanket
fields.description: Elevate your comfort with the WARMSTORM Electric Blanket. Crafted from plush Polar Fleece, it's designed to keep you cozy on chilly nights. With a voltage rating of US120V and a power output of 110W, it ensures the perfect level of warmth. Customize your comfort with 10 adjustable heat settings and enjoy the convenience of a 12-hour timer. What sets it apart is the ability to control temperature and timer settings via our user-friendly app. Plus, when it's time for a refresh, rest easy knowing it's machine washable for effortless maintenance.
fields.bullet_1: SMART REMOTE CONTROL - You can turn on the heated blanket from anywhere，anytime, after pairing with the Smart Life app via 2.4G WiFi. When you are in your living room or office, you can remotely control to turn on the WiFi electric blanket in your bedroom to preheat or turn off. NOTE: Only support 2.4G WiFi.
fields.bullet_2: Set a specific time through the schedule in the Smart Life app to turn the electric blanket twin size on or off for you in advance. You can set a schedule to preheat your bed every day before you go to bed.
fields.bullet_3: ETL FCC certified WiFi heated blanket twin with advanced safety protection technology. Designed with 1-12 hours timer setting and temperature monitoring, flame retardant protection, overheating protection, short circuit protection to provide a safer and more secure warming experience.
fields.bullet_4: The twin electric blanket is made of skin-friendly flannel, which is very soft to the touch and durable, without pilling or fading. Great thermal insulated ability to ensure maximum warmth and comfort. Removal controller can also be used as a regular blanket for year-round use.
fields.bullet_5: 3-minute fast heating technology allows you to get warm and comfortable without long waiting time. The electric blanket twin is made of NTC/PVC high temperature resistant heating wire with even heat distribution, which can always maintain consistent comfort and warmth during use
fields.textile_dry_recommendation: Line Dry or Lay Flat to Dry

fields.description: Elevate your comfort with the WARMSTORM Electric Blanket. Crafted from plush Polar Fleece, it's designed to keep you cozy on chilly nights. With a voltage rating of US120V and a power output of 110W, it ensures the perfect level of warmth. Customize your comfort with 10 adjustable heat settings and enjoy the convenience of a 12-hour timer. What sets it apart is the ability to control temperature and timer settings via our user-friendly app. Plus, when it's time for a refresh, rest easy knowing it's machine washable for effortless maintenance.
fields.bullet_1: SMART REMOTE CONTROL - You can turn on the heated blanket from anywhere，anytime, after pairing with the Smart Life app via 2.4G WiFi. When you are in your living room or office, you can remotely control to turn on the WiFi electric blanket in your bedroom to preheat or turn off. NOTE: Only support 2.4G WiFi.
fields.bullet_2: Set a specific time through the schedule in the Smart Life app to turn the electric blanket twin size on or off for you in advance. You can set a schedule to preheat your bed every day before you go to bed.
fields.bullet_3: ETL FCC certified WiFi heated blanket twin with advanced safety protection technology. Designed with 1-12 hours timer setting and temperature monitoring, flame retardant protection, overheating protection, short circuit protection to provide a safer and more secure warming experience.
fields.bullet_4: The twin electric blanket is made of skin-friendly flannel, which is very soft to the touch and durable, without pilling or fading. Great thermal insulated ability to ensure maximum warmth and comfort. Removal controller can also be used as a regular blanket for year-round use.
fields.bullet_5: 3-minute fast heating technology allows you to get warm and comfortable without long waiting time. The electric blanket twin is made of NTC/PVC high temperature resistant heating wire with even heat distribution, which can always maintain consistent comfort and warmth during use

fields.name: WARMSTORM Electric Polar Fleece Throw Blanket
fields.description: Indulge in warmth and comfort with the WARMSTORM Electric Blanket. Crafted from a luxurious blend of Polar Fleece fabric, it's designed to keep you cozy on chilly nights. With a voltage of 120V and a power output of 110W, it offers just the right amount of warmth. Customize your comfort with 5 adjustable heat settings, and enjoy the convenience of a 4-hour auto-off timer for added safety and peace of mind. When it's time for a refresh, simply toss it in the washing machine, as it's machine washable for effortless maintenance.
fields.bullet_1: 5 Heat Stteings & Multipurpose - The heated throw blanket has 5 heat settings (68°F-128°F) to easily adjust to the level of warmth you want. The 8.5ft cord offers maximum flexibility and is ideal for use in bed and on the sofa, in the study and in the office
fields.bullet_2: Fast & Even Heating - 3-minute fast heating technology allows you to get warm and comfortable without long waiting time. The electric throw blanket is made of high temperature resistant heating wire with even heat distribution, which can always maintain consistent comfort and warmth during use.
fields.bullet_3: Safe - ETL & FCC certified heated blanket with advanced safety protection technology and NTC/PVC high temperature resistant heating wire. Designed with 4 hours auto off and temperature monitoring, overheating and flame retardant protection, short circuit protection to provide a safer and more secure warming experience.
fields.bullet_4: Comfortable Material - The electric blanket throw is made of skin-friendly shaper & polar fleece, which is very soft to the touch and durable, without pilling or fading. Great thermal insulated ability to ensure maximum warmth and comfort. Removal controller can also be used as a regular blanket for year-round use.
fields.bullet_5: Easy to Care & 3 Years Warranty- Heating blanket throw is machine washable. When using electric blankets, please read the manual in detail. If you encounter any problems,please contact us. We are always here to help you.

fields.name: WARMSTORM Heated Knee Blanket
fields.description: Experience versatile comfort with the WARMSTORM Flannelette Heated Blanket. Powered by 5V, it's compatible with both plug-in and power banks, providing warmth wherever you need it. With 3 adjustable heat settings, you can personalize your comfort. Safety is paramount with a 2-hour timer and automatic shutdown in case of abnormalities. And for easy maintenance, it's machine washable. This multi-purpose design can be used as a shawl, knee blanket, or nap blanket, making it the perfect companion for any occasion.
fields.bullet_1: 【Cordless & Portable】The 40'' x 30'' heated blanket throw is powered by battery(not included). It allows you to be free from the limitation of cords and go anywhere. The electric throw blanket very suitable for outdoors, fishing, camping, watching games, travel, car, home and office
fields.bullet_2: 【Shoulder Buckle Design】Designed with special shoulder buckles, the heated blanket battery operated can be kept on your shoulder. You can move freely without worries.
fields.bullet_3: 【3 Heating levels & 2-hour Auto-off】The usb heated blanket features with 3 heating levels to mee your needs. 2-hour auto-off function ensures your safety.
fields.bullet_4: 【Comfortable & Warm】This battery operated heated blanket is made of skin-friendly and soft micro-polyester which helps effectively prevent heat from losing and keeps you warm.
fields.bullet_5: 【Easy Care】The cordless heated throw blanket is machine washable. Please remove the battery before washing. If you have any questions, please feel free to contact us.

fields.name: ACTBEST Core E-Bike
fields.description: Experience urban commuting redefined with the Actbest Core E-Bike. Designed with a potent 500W brushless motor, this commuter gem glides at speeds of up to 22MPH, supported by a 7-speed transmission and versatile 26'' tires. Its three distinct riding modes promise adaptability for every journey. The UL-certificated 36V 13AH battery, not only showcases waterproof and shockproof capabilities but also rejuvenates swiftly in 4-6 hours, offering up to 50 miles of pedal-assisted travel. Crafted from robust aluminum alloy, its step-thru design elegantly accommodates riders from 5'4" to 6'5" while the adjustable Selle Royal seat ensures comfort. Stay informed on-the-go with its intuitive LCD, which presents essential ride metrics and includes a handy USB port. With impeccable front and rear disc brakes, dual suspension, and safety lighting, the Core doesn’t compromise on safety. Delivered 90% pre-assembled and backed by a 12-month warranty, the Actbest Core is your next-gen ticket to the city's heartbeat.
fields.bullet_1: Novel Commuter E-Bike with 3 Riding Modes- Powerful 500W brushless motor, speed up to 22MPH, with 7-speed transmission, 26'' tires and 3 riding modes including manual, pedal-assisted and pure electric, helps you smoothly navigate through various terrains even mild hilly areas, during commuting, traveling, and sightseeing
fields.bullet_2: Removable Built-in Battery :The UL-certificated 36V 13AH battery is easy to remove for charging and has a waterproof, shockproof design,which is safer and lasts much longer than other. The battery only takes 4-6 hours to fully charge, giving you a range of up to 35 miles (throttle)/50 miles (PAS) on a single charge.
fields.bullet_3: Adjustable and Durable Step-Thru Cityrun Ebike - The height of the comfy Selle Royal seat cushion can be adjusted to fit people of different heights (5'4"-6'5"), and the aluminum alloy body is lightweight, solid and durable, can bear up to 350lbs.
fields.bullet_4: Enhanced Riding Experience: The Core electric bike is equipped with an LCD screen that displays key information such as speed, battery level, and assist level, making it easy for you to track your ride, USB charging port for convenient use. Our bike also features excellent front and rear disc brake systems that provide all-weather braking performance, dual front suspension with key, front and rear safety lights, and a 5-level pedal assist for a comfortable and safe riding experience.
fields.bullet_5: Easy Installation & Warranty - Actbest E-bikes Model Core, is almost 90% assembled and come with instructions and tools. The product comes with a 12-month warranty. If you have any other questions, please contact us, our professional customer support team will provide you with corresponding solutions. Included Components: E Bike Accessory Kit
fields.assembly_details: Adult Assembly Required, Tools Provided

fields.name: ACTBEST Knight E-Bike
fields.description: Embrace a new chapter of mobility with the Actbest Knight Folding E-Bike. Engineered with a commanding 750W brushless motor, the Knight propels you at speeds of 28MPH+ while smoothly tackling inclines above 35 degrees. Its three customizable riding modes ensure adaptability across diverse terrains. The detachable 720WH (48V 15Ah) battery, equipped with intelligent BMS-level tech, ensures unmatched safety and durability, powering your adventures for up to 65 miles, and with its 3A rapid charge, you're back on the road in just 3-5 hours. Designed from resilient aluminum alloy, and grounded by 4.0 fat tires, the Knight guarantees a steady ride, complemented by a versatile rear rack. Its foldable step-thru architecture caters to riders between 5'3" and 6'6", promising personalized comfort. fields.name: NEO Chair N-gen Gaming Chair
fields.description: Elevate your gaming experience with N-GEN's Next Generation Gaming Chairs. We're not just offering you a seat; we're delivering a gaming throne, meticulously crafted with an unwavering commitment to detail. Packed with cutting-edge features, our chairs guarantee the ultimate in comfort, style, and performance, enhancing every gaming session. Designed to cater to your needs, N-GEN gaming chairs create an immersive gaming environment that allows you to fully immerse yourself in your favorite games. Say goodbye to discomfort and hello to gaming excellence!
fields.bullet_1: Each body is unique. Instead of a fixed lumbar support cushion, N-GEN's LEVIS is upgraded with an adjustable lumbar cushion. Both the head and lumbar cushions are removable for versatile customization.
fields.bullet_2: Feel the difference with N-GEN's signature seat design. Fullest fill for all-day comfort. Slightly contoured leveled seat for balanced support. Sit any way you like with the extra space.
fields.bullet_3: Made with soft & high-quality multi-layered PU leather. Resistant to scratches, stains, peeling, and cracking for easy maintenance. Finished with detailed embroidery.
fields.bullet_4: Smooth-rolling wheels. Durable & smooth gas lift cylinder. Powerfully supportive base. All tested over 10,000 times and certified for safety and quality.

fields.name: Paris Rhône 14L Air Oven
fields.description: Experience hassle-free cooking with our convenient, open design featuring 3 easy-to-use knobs and a transparent glass lid for simple monitoring. With a 14-quart capacity complemented by extra accessories, there’s ample space to fry a feast for the whole family. Cater to all your culinary needs with 5 versatile cooking modes: air fry, toast, bake, roast, and warm. Achieve perfectly even cooking thanks to top and bottom heating elements and 360° air circulation. And when it’s time to clean up, there’s no mess and no fuss with the non-stick coating that makes cleaning a breeze.
fields.bullet_1: Convenient, open design: 3 knobs, transparent glass lid, easy monitoring.
fields.bullet_2: Fry a feast: 14-quart capacity, extra accessories, ample space.
fields.bullet_3: 5 modes to cook everything: air fry, toast, bake, roast, warm.
fields.bullet_4: Ensures even heat: top and bottom heating, 360° air circulation.
fields.bullet_5: No mess, no fuss cleaning: non-stick coating, easy to clean.

fields.name: TaoTronics TT-DL1004 Gooseneck LED Desk Lamp with 3 Color Temperatures and Touch-Control Brightness
fields.description: Enjoy complete lighting control with our LED desk lamp. Choose from 3 color temperatures and adjust brightness for various activities. Premium LEDs provide flicker-free illumination for up to 50,000 hours. At night, the gentle Night Light mode won't strain your eyes, and a 1-hour timer saves energy. Built-in safeguards ensure safety, and user-friendly features include an adjustable lamp arm and automatic restoration of your preferred settings. Illuminate your workspace with ease and style.
fields.bullet_1: Customizable Brightness Level & Color Temperature: Tap on the touch control panel to select from 3 color temperatures, and run your finger over the dimmer strip to choose from multiple brightness levels to suit activities such as reading, handcrafts, study, etc.
fields.bullet_2: Premium LEDs cast an even and non-flickering light on your desk and last up to 50000 hours.
fields.bullet_3: Ease of Use at Night: Night light mode shines a gentle light that doesn’t irritate your eyes; turn on the 1-hour timer before you go to bed to save precious energy.
fields.bullet_4: Reliable Protection: Built-in safeguards protect against overvoltage problems in order to provide you with a safe LED desk lamp for you and your family.
fields.bullet_5: User-Friendly Features: Adjustable lamp arm offers maximum mobility to cast light anywhere; the lamp automatically restores the previous color and brightness settings for your convenience.
fields.assembly_details: No Assembly Required
fields.light_settings: Dimmable (Full Range with Distinct Levels of Brightness)

fields.name: VAVA VA-CL1001 Chicken LED Night Light, Built-In White Noise
fields.description: The VAVA night light is a versatile companion for parents, featuring 8 soothing melodies and a gentle night light. Made from safe materials suitable for toys, it's designed with children in mind. Compact and portable, it's ideal for various situations, including camping. With a 30-minute night mode for a quality sleep, this user-friendly lamp offers touch controls for on/off and brightness adjustment. It boasts an integrated rechargeable battery, providing up to 150 hours of low light, 40 hours of melody playback, or 20 hours of combined light and music use. The package includes a USB charging cable for your convenience.
fields.bullet_1: The VAVA night light with 8 different melodies is a great helper for feeding the baby and changing diapers. Using it as a night light, you can watch your child in the dim twilight at night without turning on the bright light in the room.
fields.bullet_2: The night lamp is made of 100% safe materials suitable for toys, and its design is suitable for children. The VAVA night light has a silicone suspension loop. Due to its compact dimensions, it is also suitable for camping, nature trips or on dark terraces.
fields.bullet_3: The device has 8 skitring (white noise) melodies: the chirping of birds, the gentle sound of bells, the rustle of waves, the sounds of cicadas, rain, the sound of water droplets, the roar of a stream and the crackling of frogs.
fields.bullet_4: To ensure a quality sleep for the child, this lamp has a night mode. When activated, the light and music turn off automatically after 30 minutes.
fields.bullet_5: The VAVA VA-CL101 music night light is a user-friendly, touch-controlled device. With a simple light touch, you can turn the lamp on or off and adjust brightness with a longer touch. It boasts an integrated rechargeable battery, delivering up to 150 hours in low light, 40 hours of melody playback, and 20 hours of combined light and music use. The package includes a USB charging cable and a set of stickers, enhancing the lamp's playful and unique appeal.
fields.assembly_details: No Assembly Required

fields.name: Sympa DL048 LED Desk Lamp with Eye Comfort, Wireless Charging
fields.description: Our table lamp offers various lighting combinations, with 7 brightness levels and 5 color temperatures to suit your needs. It's gentle on your eyes, providing a soft and flicker-free light to prevent eye fatigue during extended work, study, or reading sessions. With highly adjustable angles, you can tilt the head up 135° and swivel 90°, and even tilt the base down to 150° and swivel 45° to direct the light precisely where you need it. The convenience of a built-in USB charging port allows you to power up your smartphone, tablet, or other USB-charged devices as you light up your room. With premium LED bulbs that last up to 50,000 hours, this lamp offers long-lasting illumination, saving you money and extending its lifespan.
fields.bullet_1: Various Lighting Combinations: Tap or slide across the Light Brightness Slider to adjust between 7 brightness levels, and tap the Color Temperature Button to select from 5 color temperatures to better accommodate your different needs
fields.bullet_2: Gentle on Your Eyes: Table lamp emits a soft and flicker-free light to relieve eye fatigue and protect your eyes while working, studying and reading for extended periods of time
fields.bullet_3: Highly Adjustable Angle: Tilt the head up 135° and swivel 90°, also you can tilt the base down to 150° and swivel 45° to place the light in any direction you need with incredible ease
fields.bullet_4: Convenient USB Charging Port: As you light your room, the LED desk lamp juices up your smartphone, tablet, e-reader or any other USB-charged device via the built-in USB output
fields.bullet_5: Long-Lasting Lighting: Premium LED bulbs provide reliable illumination for up to 50000 hours, approximately 50x longer than other types of incandescent bulbs, effectively extending the lifespan and saving you money

fields.name: ASPIRON Bagless Lightweight Canister Vacuum Cleaner
fields.description: The ASPIRON Bagless Canister Vacuum makes it easy to take powerful mess removal from one room in your home to another. Featuring cyclonic technology that provides powerful, continuous suction across both low pile carpets and hard floors. The compact, portable and lightweight design along with tight turn steering make maneuvering around furniture and between rooms a snap. The included tools and 30.7 inch telescopic wand let you clean those hard-to-reach areas of your home with ease.

fields.bullet_3: Anti-Allergen 3-Stage Filtration Technology and HEPA filter
fields.bullet_4: Ideal low pile carpet and hard floor vacuum cleaner
fields.bullet_5: Extra large capacity 3.5L washable dirt cup

fields.name: Evajoy Full-Sized Electric Heated Blanket
fields.description: Discover cozy, certified comfort with our plush flannel electric blanket, featuring 10 heat settings and a 3-hour auto shutoff for effortless relaxation. ETL-certified for safety and designed for convenience, it's easily washable and durable, ensuring long-term, hygienic warmth.
fields.bullet_1: Crafted from plush flannel, this comforting and cozy heated blanket brings you a warm hug whenever you need.
fields.bullet_2: Choose your desired comfort from 10 temperatures and 3 timer settings with the handy controller; disconnect before washing.
fields.bullet_3: Electric throw blanket with reliable overheating protection, ETL certification, and auto shutoff after 3 hours to fall asleep with ease.
fields.bullet_4: Conveniently clean and care for your blanket by loading into the washer or dryer to keep it hygienic and use for years to come.

fields.name: TaoTronics Metal Gooseneck Floor Lamp
fields.description: Illuminate your space with versatility using our standing lamp, designed to blend seamlessly into any activity. Mix and match with 4 color temperatures and brightness levels to tailor your lighting needs. Enjoy a generous 8.5 x 1.8-inch lighting area, perfect for detailed tasks like reading, sewing, or crafting. The energy-efficient, long-lasting LED bulb delivers up to 1000 lux & 450lm of bright, cool light. Position light precisely with the adjustable 69.3-inch gooseneck. Plus, the wide, square base ensures stability in any space, making it a smart addition to your home or workshop.
fields.bullet_1: Mix 4 color temperatures with 4 brightness levels to create the most suitable lighting for your environment or activity
fields.bullet_2: A broad 8. 5 x 1. 8” lighting area casts radiant light on activities including reading, sewing, wood working and arts & crafts
fields.bullet_3: Long-lasting LED bulb consumes as little as 10W of power and projects up to 1000 lux & 450lm, for awe-inspiring light that produces no heat
fields.bullet_4: Comfortably casts light from a 69. 3” height; rotatable gooseneck is designed to precisely direct light where it is most needed
fields.bullet_5: Wide, square base is sturdy and prevents the lamp from being knocked over, even in awkward spaces
fields.assembly_details: No Assembly Required
fields.light_bulb_base_or_socket_size: Standard Edison Medium Screw Base E26

fields.name: HOMLUX 2 Tier Individual Pull Out Cabinet Organizer
fields.description: Elevate your kitchen storage with our 2-Tier Silver Metal Individual Pull Out Cabinet Organizer. Designed with utmost precision and functionality in mind, this sleek silver organizer promises not only aesthetic appeal but also exceptional utility.Constructed with high-quality metal, it offers durability that stands the test of time, while its silver finish gives a modern and stylish touch to any cabinet. Its two-tier design allows for optimum space utilization, ensuring that you can store various kitchen essentials efficiently. Smooth gliding rails promise a seamless experience every time you pull out or push in the organizer.Installation is a breeze, fitting seamlessly into most standard-sized cabinets.Bring home organization and elegance in one go with this essential kitchen addition.Always ensure compatibility with your cabinet dimensions before purchasing.

fields.name: 96-Pack 1500 Lumen LED A19 Bulbs 100W Bright white/Daylight/Soft white
fields.description: The 96-pack of A19 LED light bulbs offers a practical and energy-efficient lighting solution for a multitude of settings. Each bulb serves as an effective replacement for traditional 100-watt incandescent bulbs, providing a bright white light with an impressive 1500 lumens output, while only using 15 watts of power. This transition to LED means you'll enjoy reduced energy consumption and significant savings on your electricity bills. fields.description: Easily add a unique touch to your home's decor with this 52 in. Indoor/Outdoor Ceiling Fan. The ultra-quiet motor is without causing too much noise to disturb your family. DIMENSION: Width: 52 inches Height: 13.7 inches with rod lengths options of 5 inches, 10 inches, and 24 inches. fields.bullet_2: This fan is sure to deliver a high-quality, quiet performance while saving energy both in the summer and winter months.

fields.bullet_4: Silent and Timer：Set the timer for 1, 2, 4, or 8 hours, allowing you to customize the operating time according to your needs.
fields.bullet_5: MADE FOR ANY SPACE: The 52-inch blade span makes this ceiling fan perfect for spaces like living rooms, bedrooms or larger bathrooms (suitable for damp places).

fields.name: HOMLUX 64"x21" Arched Leaning Floor Mirror Oversized Full Length Bathroom Mirror
fields.description: Showcasing a 64" x 21" full-size mirror, our design guarantees a comprehensive reflection, illuminating your appearance and boosting your confidence. The distinct smooth arched-top frame, a highlight of its design, captivates attention and amplifies the mirror's elegance. Complemented by a slender aluminum alloy frame, it exudes a timeless charm, fitting seamlessly into any room's decor. Prioritizing clarity, the mirror employs high-grade float glass for a pristine, undistorted image. Safety isn't compromised, with an explosion-proof membrane ensuring that even if damaged, shards won't scatter. Whether leaning against a wall or standing solo, its sturdy frame promises durability. Your contentment is paramount, and if any issues arise, our 24/7 customer support is ready to ensure complete satisfaction
fields.bullet_1: Full-Length Mirror: This is a 64"x21" full-size mirror, enough for you to see your entire figure in a single glance and bring you light, beauty, and confidence
fields.bullet_2: Unique Design: The top of the floor mirror is designed with a unique smooth arched-top frame, which especially attracts people's attention and highlights the beauty of the mirror. The thin aluminum alloy frame makes the mirror looks more classic and it is suitable for dressing in any room
fields.bullet_3: High-quality Glass: The full body mirror is made of high-quality float glass which can provide super HD imaging and undistorted reflection. The back is covered with an explosion-proof membrane so that it's safer. Even it is accidentally damaged by an external force, the broken pieces of mirror will not splash in all directions
fields.bullet_4: Easy Installation: Our full-length mirrors can be leaned to the wall or free-standing with the stand anywhere in your room. The aluminum alloy frame is very stable and durable for your daily use
fields.bullet_5: 100% Satisfaction Customer Service: If the mirror is damaged when it arrives, or you don't absolutely love our product, please contact us in time and we'll offer you 24/7 customer service and 100% satisfaction guaranteed

fields.name: HOMLUX Round Bathroom Vanity Mirror Wall Mount Decorative Make-up Mirror Entryway
fields.description: The HOMLUX Round Wall Mirror is a testament to minimalist beauty and functional design. With its sleek, circular silhouette, it serves as a versatile piece that enhances the aesthetic of any room, from the bathroom to the bedroom, or even a stylish entryway. Crafted with meticulous attention to detail, this mirror features a high-quality aluminum alloy frame that promises durability and a timeless appeal. The simple, yet secure, hook design ensures easy installation, allowing the mirror to become a part of your home decor with minimal effort.
fields.bullet_1: Streamlined Elegance: The HOMLUX Round Wall Mirror's understated design is perfect for creating a focal point in any room without overwhelming the space, its round shape bringing a softness to contemporary and traditional decors alike.
fields.bullet_2: Sturdy Aluminum Frame: Constructed with a high-quality aluminum alloy, the frame of this mirror provides a lightweight yet durable structure that is resistant to corrosion, ensuring the mirror's longevity even in humid environments such as bathrooms.
fields.bullet_3: Effortless Installation: This mirror's easy-to-install hook design is a significant advantage, offering the ability to quickly and securely mount the mirror without the need for professional help, making it a convenient choice for those who value simplicity and time.
fields.bullet_4: Multipurpose Decor Piece: Whether you're looking for a practical bathroom vanity mirror, a welcoming piece in your entryway, or an accent in your living space, this mirror's clean lines and classic style make it suitable for a wide range of uses throughout your home.
fields.bullet_5: Reflective Clarity: The HOMLUX Round Wall Mirror is made with precision-engineered float glass, providing a flawless reflection without warping or distortion, so you can trust that you'll see a true-to-life image every time you look into it.

fields.description: The HOMLUX Round Wall Mirror is a testament to minimalist beauty and functional design. With its sleek, circular silhouette, it serves as a versatile piece that enhances the aesthetic of any room, from the bathroom to the bedroom, or even a stylish entryway. Crafted with meticulous attention to detail, this mirror features a high-quality aluminum alloy frame that promises durability and a timeless appeal. The simple, yet secure, hook design ensures easy installation, allowing the mirror to become a part of your home decor with minimal effort.
fields.bullet_1: Streamlined Elegance: The HOMLUX Round Wall Mirror's understated design is perfect for creating a focal point in any room without overwhelming the space, its round shape bringing a softness to contemporary and traditional decors alike.
fields.bullet_2: Sturdy Aluminum Frame: Constructed with a high-quality aluminum alloy, the frame of this mirror provides a lightweight yet durable structure that is resistant to corrosion, ensuring the mirror's longevity even in humid environments such as bathrooms.
fields.bullet_3: Effortless Installation: This mirror's easy-to-install hook design is a significant advantage, offering the ability to quickly and securely mount the mirror without the need for professional help, making it a convenient choice for those who value simplicity and time.
fields.bullet_4: Multipurpose Decor Piece: Whether you're looking for a practical bathroom vanity mirror, a welcoming piece in your entryway, or an accent in your living space, this mirror's clean lines and classic style make it suitable for a wide range of uses throughout your home.
fields.bullet_5: Reflective Clarity: The HOMLUX Round Wall Mirror is made with precision-engineered float glass, providing a flawless reflection without warping or distortion, so you can trust that you'll see a true-to-life image every time you look into it.
